{"tid":480914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女友嬲我唔射佢","createTime":"2017-11-26T15:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T05:24:06.000Z","uid":157688,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7e729cd8d09456ddf4cdfa2a405b9a4189a32674","tid":480914,"uid":157688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:26:03.000Z","msg":"其實我好咸濕<br />\n成日都想搞佢<br />\n但呢排試過兩次我插插下軟左 射唔到<br />\n佢就好嬲 嬲到走左.. <br />\n其實我唔明 <br />\n佢話下次我唔射就唔好搞佢<br />\n其實我射唔射對佢有咩影響<br />\n我唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到而家每次都好大壓力<br />\n壓力大到更加難射<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f92ca6a43db9b20c2209dcaeaa7c7cc1bca5da","tid":480914,"uid":146453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7829c74708e10ff7c2e369f9adbfae356c86025","tid":480914,"uid":61622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:29:10.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6595f40cad215d050678bf0d96bd3a788c3cad31","tid":480914,"uid":116816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e856644d18e8401e2ce74d7afb438f7617859be","tid":480914,"uid":157688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:32:22.000Z","msg":"我有時淨係想插下果種快感 <br />\n又唔會想射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abd1a647cfd366a12fc5688eb047b46f3ec8bb0","tid":480914,"uid":157688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"真心唔明佢嬲咩9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba38f952e2e1b474d450b34edf736c2db86fbe1b","ti