 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18c00fb4ee44727bcc7b43503e8928e00f02189","tid":480914,"uid":157688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T18:08:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對女人黎講係侮辱啦 好似送上門你都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌呀 次次都屌起碼十分鐘<br />\n但最後有無野出係咪真係咁緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9341557ad38f1af11a7b4ceca93a8168f6bbf7f2","tid":480914,"uid":157688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T18:44:44.000Z","msg":"如果想多d精 食咩好"},{"pid":"62e5d555bdfb5d030969b1397d55b59d552811de","tid":480914,"uid":17628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T18:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果想多d精 食咩好</blockquote><br />\n精"},{"pid":"5c12d58e6f8626c52a340f23e56f38766818da4f","tid":480914,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T18:50:42.000Z","msg":"少啲叫雞揼邪啦"},{"pid":"30b66be39f47042f5c1d6e7014ac9d32a33e85d2","tid":480914,"uid":157688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:01:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少啲叫雞揼邪啦</blockquote><br />\n無叫喇 係耐唔中推下油姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429b4d0450b8ba0d34ffc303518856b215c1972d","tid":480914,"uid":132361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:07:07.000Z","msg":"可能對佢黎講 射係一種完結 係一種代表你嘅行動<br />\n你唔射 就等於佢問你你愛唔愛佢然後你答唔愛咁大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">係啊女人就係咁麻煩</span>"},{"pid":"2abc61fb67ffad3b6a2725b2cb6b49c16afdf1cc","tid":480914,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:10:28.000Z","msg":"你唔射佢點樣做<span style=\"color: green;\">爸爸</span>？"},{"pid":"46c878db2d67d57a5e64d9c6cc18e445be7956d4","tid":480914,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19: